quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  16,109,"Shaki ma leh, inay Aakhirada ahaan kuwa khasaari."
  16,110,"Rabbigaase, kuwa soo haajira kaddib inta la dhibay markaas jihaaday ee samray, hubaal Rabbigaa intaas kaddib, waa Denbi Dhaaf Badane, Naxariis Badan."
  16,111,"(Xusuuso) Maalintay naf walba imaan iyadoo u doodaysa nafteeda, oo naf walba loo oofin waxay fashay, iyagoo aan la dulmineyn."
  17,76,"Waxayna u dhowaadeen inay kaa fiijiyaan arlada si ay kaaga saaraan. markaas ma negaadeen gadaashaa in yar ma’ahee{2}.",1:[. Hadday saari lahaayeen reer Makkah Nabi Muxammad s.c.w. ma ku sii negaadeen Makkah oo wax badan ma joogeen dunida, balse Alle wuu halaagi lahaa dhammantood. Hijridii Nabiga s.c.w. ee Madiina ma ahayn saarid ay saareen Quraysh, waxayse ahayd Amar Alle uu ku amray. Ummad kasta oo saarta Nabigeeda Alle wuu halaagaa, taasina waa jid soo jireen ah aan marnaba is beddelin.],2:[]
  17,77,"(Kani waa) jidkayaga xagga Rususha aan soo dirnay hortaa, kamana heleysid wax isbeddel ah jidkayaga."
  17,78,"Oog salaadda markay qorraxdu waareegto (salaadaha Duhurka iyo Casarka) ilaa mugdiga habeenka (salaadaha Maghribka iyo Cishaha) oo (dheeree) akhrinta (salaadda) subaxa hore (salaadda Fajarka); hubaal akhrinta (salaadda) subaxa hore waa mid la soo xaadiro (ay soo xaadiraan malaa’igta habeenka iyo malaa’igta maalinta){2}.",1:[. Aayaddan waxay caddeyneysaa waqtiyada shanta salaadood, cadceed wareegga kaddib waxaa la tukadaa Salaadaha Duhurka iyo Casarka, markuu habeenka soo galana Salaadaha Maghrib iyo Cishaha, ooggana salaadda Subax.],2:[]
  18,43,"Uma ahaanin koox u gargaarta Alle sokadi, mana aha mid gargaarta."
  18,44,"Halkaasi{2}, awood oo dhan waxaa leh Allaah, Xaqa ah. Isagaa u abaal marin wanaagsan oo u cidhib wanaagsan.",1:[. Waqtigaas ama Maalinta Qiyaamaha],2:[]
  18,45,"Ugu soo qaad tusaale nolosha adduunkan inay la mid tahay biyaha aan ka soo dejinno daruuraha, markaa dhirta ka soo baxda dhulka noqoto mid isku darsanta, haddana noqota xaabo engeg ah u burburta gaballo ay dabeyshu firdhiso, Allena wuxuu ku leeyahay awood wax walba dushood."
  19,4,"Wuxuu yidhi: “Rabbiyow, anigu way daciifeen lafahaygii filweyni darteed, madaxeyguna wuxuu la wada huray (caddaaday) cirro, mana aheyn baryadayda aan ku baryo Rabbiyow mid ku qada."
  19,5,"Waxaana u cabsan xigtada{2} iga dambeysa (inay xumaadaan), marwadeyduna waa ma dhaleys. Ee iga sii Xaggaaga wali (walad)*.",1:[. Qaraabada dhinaca aabbaha ah*Si uu u dhaxlo xilka diinta, cilmiga, iyo hoggaaminta ilmo Israa’iil.],2:[]
  19,6,"I dhaxla{2}, dhaxlana reer Yacquub oo ka yeel Rabbiyow midaad ka raalli tahay.",1:[. Iga dhaxla cilmiga diinta iyo Nabinnimada ee loola ma jeedo maalka, waayo anbiyadu lagama dhaxlo maal adduunyo, waxay ka tagaan oo maal ahna waa sadaqo.],2:[]
